Dr. Do Shin Jae, si penjudi.

723
00:45:27,436 --> 00:45:28,697
Hai, Hae Ra.

724
00:45:28,697 --> 00:45:31,736
Aku ingat siapa dia.

725
00:45:32,307 --> 00:45:33,736
Dia adalah penjudi.

726
00:45:33,936 --> 00:45:34,936
Aku mendengar dia dipecat...

727
00:45:34,936 --> 00:45:36,706
